quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,70,Ɓe mbii du'ano min Joom maa O laɓɓinana min no nge wa'i sabu na'i ɗi nanndiri min maa min njiitu nge
  2,71,"O wi'i Kanko dee O wii ko nagge ne'iraange golle remru ngesa, kono wonaa yarnude gese, ko hisnge nge jillaani, ɓe mbii jooni dey a addii goonga ɓe kirsi nge kono ɓe ɗeɓaani waɗde yamiroore nde"
  2,72,Nde mbar-ɗon fettaandu ngon-ɗon e tuumondirde ko Alla yaltini ko cuuɗno-ɗon
  2,73,Min mbii tappindiree ɗi ko noon Alla wuurtinirta maayɓe O holla on kaawase Makko mbela joo kakkilon
  2,74,"Fawii heen ɓerɗe maɓɓe ɗe njoori ɓaawo ɗuum ɗe mba'i no kaaƴe maa ɓura noon, sabu kaaƴe na ngoodi jaltinooje caalli goɗɗe na peecoo njaltina ndiyam goɗɗe kadi njowtoo janansabu hulde Alla, Alla noo yeebotaako ko ngolloton ko"
  2,75,Mbela oɗon ɗaminii maa ɓe ngoonɗinan on tawa na woodi e maɓɓe sete nanoowo haala Alla ɓe mbaylita ka caggal nde ɓe paami ɓe nganndi ka
  2,76,"So ɓe kawri e goonɗinɓe ɓee ɓe mbii min ngoonɗinii so ɓe njeewdii ɓe mbi'a mbela on kaalanat ɓe ko Alla udditani on, ndeen ɓe kaɓora on ɗum to Jooma mon, mbela on kakkilantaa"